snippet.title: Indigo 7 Quest For Love - Console Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Easy to learn, hard to master! Indigo 7 is a fast-paced multiplayer puzzle game for up to 4 players, with a cool single-player story mode.

Wear your swimsuit, dust off your beach tennis rackets, and put batteries in your old radio to enjoy this cool puzzle game.
